-- Toyota U.S. December sales down 1.7 percent
-- 
-- Thu Jan 3, 2008 2:00pm EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/01/03/us-usa-autosales-toyota-idUSN0323528520080103

 

 DETROIT  (Reuters) - Toyota Motor Corp ( 7203.T ) said on Thursday its U.S. sales fell 1.7 percent in December. 

 Toyota-brand sales were down 0.7 percent. Sales for the company's luxury Lexus unit were down 7.2 percent, Toyota said. For the full-year, Toyota's U.S. sales rose 2.7 percent, it said. (Reporting by  Poornima Gupta ; Editing by  Derek Caney )